imdb.plot outline: In this episode of Stylings, we follow Puth and stylist Comrie as the duo prepare for Puth's performance at the Fonda Theatre. "I like waking up and not figuring out what I have to wear because I have music on my mind all the time," says Puth.
imdb.title: Stylings: Comfort, Music and Charlie Puth
